{"title":"hexo使用","uid":"be29bb0db4085d04ddb5f9bb082efc87","slug":"第二篇博客","date":"2023-05-01T15:12:47.000Z","updated":"2023-05-02T07:28:56.258Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/第二篇博客.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"hexo主题配置\"><a href=\"#hexo主题配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo主题配置\"></a>hexo主题配置</h2><h3 id=\"任意主题的基本配置流程\"><a href=\"#任意主题的基本配置流程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"任意主题的基本配置流程\"></a>任意主题的基本配置流程</h3><ul>\n<li>git clone 主题仓库地址 themes&#x2F;主题名</li>\n<li>修改配置文件：<ul>\n<li>打开Blog文件夹下的_config.yml文件</li>\n<li>修改theme部分：theme: 主题名</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>保存配置文件</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"使用Aurora主题\"><a href=\"#使用Aurora主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用Aurora主题\"></a>使用Aurora主题</h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>大部分主题的功能都是使用主题配置文件的，但是有部分需要用到 Hexo 插件的就需要在 Hexo 的配置中修改。</p></blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"安装并修改Aurora主题\"><a href=\"#安装并修改Aurora主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装并修改Aurora主题\"></a>安装并修改Aurora主题</h4><ol>\n<li>安装Aurora主题<ul>\n<li>在blog文件夹下打开终端</li>\n<li>安装主题：npm install hexo-theme-aurora –save</li>\n<li>在 node_modules 目录下的 hexo-theme-aurora 主题文件夹中复制 _config.yml 文件到根目录下，并重命名为 _config.aurora.yml</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>修改Aurora配置文件<ul>\n<li>打开 _config.aurora.yml 文件</li>\n<li>站点基础设置<ul>\n<li>设置site参数<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>选项</th>\n<th>子属性</th>\n<th>接受类型</th>\n<th>使用说明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>subtitle</td>\n<td>&#x2F;</td>\n<td>String</td>\n<td>博客自标题，页面主标题后面会跟随这个标题内容。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>author</td>\n<td>&#x2F;</td>\n<td>String</td>\n<td>博客作者名字，或者是博客名字。会在 header 的 logo 区域显示，也会在博客简介中显示。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>nick</td>\n<td>&#x2F;</td>\n<td>String</td>\n<td>博客子名字，会在 header 的 logo 下方显示。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>description</td>\n<td>&#x2F;</td>\n<td>String</td>\n<td>会在博客简介中显示，用几句话描述博主相关信息（支持 HTML 标签）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>language</td>\n<td>&#x2F;</td>\n<td>en, cn</td>\n<td>配置默认博客语言，en 是英文，cn 是中文。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>multi_language</td>\n<td>&#x2F;</td>\n<td>true, false</td>\n<td>开启博客的多语言支持</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>logo</td>\n<td>&#x2F;</td>\n<td>String</td>\n<td>Logo 的图片链接 image.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>avatar</td>\n<td>&#x2F;</td>\n<td>String</td>\n<td>头像的图片链接 image.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>beian</td>\n<td>&#x2F;</td>\n<td>Object</td>\n<td>网站备案信息 (从版本 1.1.0 开始，这个配置拥有两个属性)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td>number</td>\n<td>String</td>\n<td>备案编号.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td>link</td>\n<td>String</td>\n<td>备案链接.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>police_beian</td>\n<td>&#x2F;</td>\n<td>Object</td>\n<td>公安部备案号</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td>number</td>\n<td>String</td>\n<td>备案编号.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td>link</td>\n<td>String</td>\n<td>备案链接.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>如果不需要备案信息，可以不设置beian、police_beian，可为空，</p></blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>站点进阶设置<ul>\n<li>设置menu参数</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"修改hexo配置文件\"><a href=\"#修改hexo配置文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改hexo配置文件\"></a>修改hexo配置文件</h4><ol start=\"0\">\n<li>打开 _config.yml 文件</li>\n<li>设置 url 和 permalink<ul>\n<li>url 为自己的博客地址<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>例如 url: <a href=\"https://kevin-lxj.github.io/\">https://kevin-lxj.github.io</a></p></blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>permalink 参数为 &#x2F;post&#x2F;:title.html<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>permalink参数的作用：指生成的博客的链接格式，例如：<a href=\"https://kevin-lxj.github.io/post/%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E7%AF%87%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2.html\">https://kevin-lxj.github.io/post/第二篇博客.html</a></p></blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>设置代码高亮<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Aurora 主题使用了 prismjs 作为代码高亮插件，如果不关闭 Highlight，会导致代码高亮两次，从而导致代码高亮失效。</p></blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>关闭 Highlight，设置 enable 为 false。</li>\n<li>使用 prismjs，设置 enable 为 true，将 preprocess 设置为 false</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>设置主题<ul>\n<li>设置 theme 为 aurora</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","feature":true,"text":"hexo主题配置任意主题的基本配置流程 git clone 主题仓库地址 themes&#x2F;主题名 修改配置文件： 打开Blog文件夹下的_config.yml文件 修改theme部分：theme: 主题名 保存配置文件 使用Aurora主题 大部分主题的功能都是使用主题配...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.5k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#hexo%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">hexo主题配置</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%8F%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">任意主题的基本配置流程</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Aurora%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">使用Aurora主题</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%B9%B6%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9Aurora%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装并修改Aurora主题</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9hexo%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">修改hexo配置文件</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Kevin","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"第一篇博客","uid":"7bcb9e1af25ded2b038f5286bb791f16","slug":"第一篇博客","date":"2023-05-01T15:12:47.000Z","updated":"2023-05-01T15:15:51.717Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/第一篇博客.json","keywords":null,"cover"